          "author": {
            "login": "ConcaveTrillion"
          },
          "body": "Context: Discovered while working on pd-ocr-cli (feat/upgrade-deps-local).\n\n`make upgrade-deps` silently clobbers an editable dev-local venv. The fix (three-tier editable detection + refuse-by-default + `upgrade-deps-local` restore recipe + `.venv/.pd-dev-local` marker) landed in pd-ocr-cli. The spec calls for lockstep across all pd-* repos with dev-local Makefile targets.\n\nSpec: https://github.com/ConcaveTrillion/pd-ocr-cli/blob/main/docs/runbooks/dev-local-upgrade-flow.md",
          "closedAt": "2026-05-25T03:22:14Z",
